#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.to_odps_table.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.to\\_odps\\_table"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:1 of
msgid "Write DataFrame object into a MaxCompute (ODPS) table."
msgstr "将 DataFrame 对象写入 MaxCompute (ODPS) 表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:3 of
msgid ""
"You need to provide the name of the table to write to. If you want to "
"store data into a specific partitioned of a table, argument `partition` "
"can be used. You can also use `partition_col` to specify DataFrame "
"columns as partition columns, and data in the DataFrame will be grouped "
"by these columns and inserted into partitions the values of these "
"columns."
msgstr ""
"您需要提供要写入的表名。如果要将数据存储到表的特定分区中，可以使用参数 `"
"partition`。您还可以使用 `partition_col` 将 DataFrame 列指定为分区列，"
"DataFrame 中的数据将按这些列分组，并根据这些列的值插入到分区中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:9 of
msgid "If the table does not exist, `to_odps_table` will create one."
msgstr "如果表不存在，`to_odps_table` 将创建一个。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:11 of
msgid ""
"Column names for indexes is determined by `index_label` argument. If the "
"argument is absent, names of the levels is used if they are not None, or "
"default names will be used. The default name for indexes with only one "
"level will be `index`, and for indexes with multiple levels, the name "
"will be `level_x` while x is the index of the level."
msgstr ""
"索引的列名由 `index_label` 参数确定。如果该参数缺失，则在级别名称不为 "
"None 时使用级别名称，否则使用默认名称。对于只有一个级别的索引，默认名称为"
" `index`，对于具有多个级别的索引，名称将为 `level_x`，其中 x 是级别的索引"
"。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.to_odps_table.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:17 of
msgid "Name ot the table to write DataFrame into"
msgstr "要将 DataFrame 写入的表名"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:19 of
msgid "Spec of the partition to write to, can be 'pt1=xxx,pt2=yyy'"
msgstr "要写入的分区规范，可以是 'pt1=xxx,pt2=yyy'"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:21 of
msgid "Name of columns in DataFrame as partition columns."
msgstr "DataFrame 中作为分区列的列名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:23 of
msgid "Overwrite data if the table / partition already exists."
msgstr "如果表/分区已存在，则覆盖数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:25 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If True, object type in the DataFrame will be treated as strings. "
"Otherwise errors might be raised."
msgstr "如果为 True，则 DataFrame 中的对象类型将被视为字符串。否则可能会引发错误。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:28 of
msgid "If True, indexes will be stored. Otherwise they are ignored."
msgstr "如果为 True，则将存储索引。否则将忽略索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:30 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Specify column names for index levels. If absent, level names or default "
"names will be used."
msgstr "指定索引级别的列名。如果缺失，则使用级别名称或默认名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:33 of
msgid "Specify lifecycle of the output table."
msgstr "指定输出表的生命周期。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:35 of
msgid "Specify properties of the output table."
msgstr "指定输出表的属性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:37 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If provided and target table does not exist, target table will be a delta"
" table with columns specified in this argument as primary key."
msgstr ""
"如果提供了此参数且目标表不存在，则目标表将是一个增量表，此参数中指定的列"
"作为主键。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.to_odps_table.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:42 of
msgid "**result** -- Stub DataFrame for execution."
msgstr "**result** -- 用于执行的空 DataFrame。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.to_odps_table.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:46 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_odps.to_odps_table:47 of
msgid ""
"`to_odps_table` returns a stub object for execution. The result returned "
"is not reusable."
msgstr "`to_odps_table` 返回一个用于执行的空对象。返回的结果不可重用。"

